action.content: DESCRIPTION: The image shows a small, narrow kitchen space with off-white walls and cabinetry. On the right, a window set deep into the wall lets in natural light, casting angular sunlit patches across the cabinets and countertop. A radiator or heater unit sits beneath the window. The overall look is utilitarian and unadorned, with clean lines and neutral tones.
